General.Name: Svenska Aerogel Holding AB (publ)
General.Description: Svenska Aerogel Holding AB (publ) engages in the research, development, production, and sale of aerogel in Europe, North America, and Asia. The company offers Quartzene which is used to enhance the performance of various products and solutions. Its products are used in transport, process, pulp and paper, and building and construction industries. The company sells its products through direct sales channels and resellers. Svenska Aerogel Holding AB (publ) was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Gävle, Sweden.
